{"tid":511931,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[招團友] 獨遊台北freehug之旅","createTime":"2017-12-28T03:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T14:13:08.000Z","uid":39878,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"787dab9070c24377ccf1714dcb7a489cb305c319","tid":511931,"uid":39878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:19:51.000Z","msg":"上年12月同屋企人去過台灣，識左個玩freehug既台仔，本來約好左上年31號一齊去101 freehug+倒數，點知電話收唔到，搵唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以今次呢個freehug之旅都plan左好耐，連塊牌都整定<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/110943_e647c6b7b220d1463881d56477a2d5d6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F110943_e647c6b7b220d1463881d56477a2d5d6.jpeg&h=c7c66d96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/110945_1bb6b4f1a21c60d5fd70eb0f6567ca50.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F110945_1bb6b4f1a21c60d5fd70eb0f6567ca50.jpeg&h=45d5fd9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日會飛過去台北，玩7日，3號早機返香港，諗住呢幾晚都會喺台北唔同地方舉牌玩freehug，西門町 台北車站 東區 信義區 101果邊都會去，暫時係一個人(當然有多d人玩就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n都係呢幾日去台北既 想約出黎玩下行下 或者join freehug都可以搵me <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/cc3221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcc3221&d=3Q0axaAZ8itZuAOIHRvp%2FS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3b509df7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cc3221</a>"},{"pid":"3793622e0c0533aeb8b7a81ff2306a1f43588e24","tid":511931,"uid":154963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今晚飛台北 見到支持下你"},{"pid":"3e35a2a20058ba2392fc0388bf22128ce57e78f7","tid":511931,"uid":23416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"影撚衰晒"},{"pid":"f81fa8d6f0bb